name: 05. ENVY
description:
5/7 from "7 Deadly Sins" collection. 

I stumble with promises out of a corner that I do not want, but blood condemns me, 
the acquired information, the lies from the show, the brainwash.
Everything takes me to the same place as if I were walking in circles. Waking up every morning with the same things, 
and the light of destiny is hidden.
 I travelled to the depths of the abyss, inside your cold body, because of decisions not taken.
 Just when the temperature was boiling you jumped out to uncover the crap. 
And I walk through paths with thorns, where I always find a way out: the first one to my right, the second straight ahead; 
make a turn then uphill and you will meet the finest view if you allow yourself the visit.

Full story: naranjabrasa.com
